Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下迷宮到底有多長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏在其深處的秘寶又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 自稱間諜的沙耶到底是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.78,0:01:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都尚不明朗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而現在 我卻感覺和她在一起的這段時間彌足珍貴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是不是見過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…從很久前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就喜歡沙耶了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底 是從什麼時候起喜歡上她的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快到地下5層了 台階應該就在附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 你看什麼看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.24,0:02:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們隨時可能襲擊過來 而你卻一點緊張感都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,門外漢就是這麼傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得這樣我們可能找得到秘寶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可得怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你盯著我看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,息怒息怒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它往下扯入口大概就會打開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我們海拔不大夠耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.66,0:03:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀借一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要騎上去 這還用問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.07,0:03:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 站起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹君 我跳上去扯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功咯!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來是尊石像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:56.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力VS力 正面交鋒是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和那玩意交戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹倒它才能繼續走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去找攻略法 附近應該有能讓它停下的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.80,0:05:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不戰誰戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧 太危險了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是專業的 沒那麼容易掛掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只會礙事 閃一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.62,0:05:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你個臭傢伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 我在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來會會你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明怕得都站不穩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹君 把劍扔過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別廢話 扔過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不扔我可發飆了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你個少年癡呆!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扭到腳了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是現在他們來襲 我們分分鐘完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放放放我下來啦 我站得起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 當著淑女的面說人家重不覺得很沒禮貌嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 丟臉丟到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,職業間諜落得個需要門外漢救的下場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.83,0:07:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太淒慘了 你乾脆嘲笑我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:07:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這裡痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你負得起責任嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家還是處女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸了處女就要負責的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一下爆出這麼大的料我哪受得起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看應該沒骨折
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 和你一起我總是不在狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你這張笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 你最好別搪塞我 你剛才趁亂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我…沙耶了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫沙耶桑也就算了 直接叫沙耶也太親暱了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想叫你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道什麼時候 不過我覺得很久前也這麼叫過你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個 理樹君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大著膽子直說了 你別太吃驚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…喜歡理樹君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.99,0:09:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…在戰場上這種情況是可以有的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在覺得超受傷的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且這股悲傷正慢慢轉化成殺意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以斃了你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 當然不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.46,0:09:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我死好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:09:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪你怪你怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不都怪你居然不肯對嘴兒!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.42,0:10:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不讓我殺了你 要不讓我自殺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想活在這種悲哀的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我不是拒絕了你 只是嚇了一跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你個大蠢蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 你說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這裡是戰場 接吻前也是要閉眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…那我就勉為其難了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知為何 我突然預感到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.72,0:11:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久後我或許會失去她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫叫看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 為啥那把劍正好出現在石像旁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:12:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不覺得這迷宮有點戲弄入侵者的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我才沒覺得害臊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,職業間諜是不會因為一個吻而動搖的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說我已經習慣接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其…其實那還是初吻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點我可沒說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就算臉紅心跳也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怪叫什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不是因為理樹君…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一臉只有我很在意的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.46,0:12:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 就當我的臀部身經百戰好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是毫不在意我就難辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就會突顯出我非常在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:01.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也…很在意啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.56,0:13:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是初次和喜歡的女生…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生怎麼能發出這種詭異的怪聲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不是你逼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 就算被逼也不會有人照做的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又…又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想你的時候跟你撞到一起我當然會嚇一跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都不懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也怪我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞得跟一對清純情侶似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攪啊攪啊攪!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 你又來…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得美少女不會做這種事對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作出羞恥發言後來個齷齪語句 這樣就互相抵消啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:14:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不會呢 女生不能說這種話的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵消不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不就只剩羞恥了嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還好吧 有沒受傷?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡…胡鬧就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡就是最後難關
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在不碰那玩意的前提下 通過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於抵達這最終決戰之地了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終決戰?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在抵達最底層的秘寶所在地前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須先在此和他一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗之執行部的幹部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是這個世界的最終BOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他應該就守在這前面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前的黑暗彷彿在告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再往前我就要和她永別了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 理樹君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得藏在這地下迷宮裡的秘寶是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說不是什麼金銀財寶 而是某種很革新的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:57.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UFO的動力引擎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 確實挺革新的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難怪美國和俄國都那麼想要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 此話當真?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚 天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶覺得是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.58,0:16:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據我推測呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘寶是時間機器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要真是如此 比UFO厲害多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若非這種利器的話 就不會有間諜從世界各地被派來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間機器啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我們得到了它 理樹君想去什麼時代呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛 我想去一百年左右後的未來確認一下文化的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.70,0:16:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定百年後地球就毀滅了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:45.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一到未來就死掉 那就太蠢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你是想回到過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可能的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回到小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後想重頭來過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重頭來過 再一次和理樹君邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 假如…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說假如
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.67,0:17:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假如這次任務順利完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能邀你去約會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行啊 就我們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我們上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑幕在等著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑幕?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像沒資格這麼說我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於現身了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗之執行部 部長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時風 瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該誇讚你們 居然能來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 變得有模有樣了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹君 不用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在叫我一個人去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡必須由我出戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦 規則如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不守規則就找不到秘寶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:18:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理樹君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定…帶你去約會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一句話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,約定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我消失!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次相戀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和理樹君…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去…約會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我第幾次死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,99次?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是更多?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我又開始等待理樹君的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 原來是樹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼晚還在校舍裡逗留
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來取落下的筆記本…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別回頭 跑到走廊盡頭 從正面逃生門出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一放手你就跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白沒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的理樹君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一的搭檔
